[list]
[*]Every round is totally different;
[*]Power-ups are creative and keep things fresh;
[*]Love being able to unlock additional ships, I'm a few hours in and still have ships to unlock;
[*]Really simple to play, but always leaves me feeling like "Just one more round, I know I can beat that score...";
[*]Great game to pick up and play when you got a little downtime, bonus for being cross platform;
[*]Controller support out of the box;
[/list]

Probably not intended by the developer, but also makes a great drinking game. Had some friends over, played 1 round at a time each, players with the highest and lowest score take a shot

